-- Italy's Azimut says August net inflows at 262 mln euros
-- By Francesca Landini
-- Mon Sep 08, 2014 08:51AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Sept 8 (Reuters) - Italian asset manager Azimut <AZMT.MI> said on Monday net inflows were 262 million euros (339.3 million US dollar) in August, bringing net inflows since the beginning of the year above 4.1 billion euros.

Total assets under management stood at 25.7 billion euros, Azimut said.